data.name: textBoxDescription.Text
data.value:
The Digitised Lemon Converter is a software tool created and used to convert other currencies to (and from) the Blepian lemon.
The first version of the DLC was created by Tablecloth Kitten on 20 December 2017 as a batch file after obtaining the idea from Windfarmer, who incidentally is creating this version of the DLC.
On the same day, Windfarmer created a graphical version of the DLC, called version 1.1, as a superior successor to the batch version.
Also on the same day, then-Blepian Potato Curry had also developed his version of the DLC, however as a command-line interface Java program. His version of the DLC is never noticed because nobody could figure out how to run it at the time.
It fell solely on Windfarmer to create the next version of the DLC, but development was very slow due to constantly restarting the project. For the entirety of 2018 and the first half of 2019, the next version of the DLC was promised but never came.
This version, the one you used to get to this page, is supposed to be that version.
